These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, teacher, project-manager, nurse
1. the nurse is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the teacher##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the project-manager is on the left or right of the nurse##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Job        | coach | teacher   | nurse | project-manager    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, skateboard, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person driving the train##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Transport   | skateboard | train  | roller  | boat |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, turtle, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Pet          | cat | turtle | ferret    | rabbit      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, doctor, librarian, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the doctor is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, photography, sudoku
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku | photography | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Transport   | skateboard | trike     | train  | bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
House: farmhouse, palace, futuristic, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the ranch-style house is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
6. the palace house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| House     | ranch-style | futuristic  | farmhouse     | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, card-games, hiking
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the goat##2
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | singing | collecting      | hiking | card-games |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, western, time-travel, scientific
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person watching time-travel movies##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | western   | comedy | time-travel |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, red, apricot
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes light-blue and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Color   | red | pink | apricot        | light-blue    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, folk, metal, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, punk-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is punk-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is punk-polo is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | punk   | folk      | metal      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | punk-polo | biathlon |

