.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, family, satire, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, gospel, reggae
1. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | satire | thriller  |
| Music-Genre     | metal   | country  | reggae  | gospel |

