.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, chinese, egyptian, italian
1. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the japanese is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the japanese is on the left or right of the italian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Nationality           | italian     | japanese     | egyptian   | chinese         |

