.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, pony, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the owner of the bird is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the hedgehog##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Pet   | hamster | hedgehog         | bird   | pony |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

