.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar, game, old-henry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the game-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
5. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | pall-mall | game    | old-henry |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

