.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
There 4 different types of food: papaya, zucchini, mango, blueberry
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person eating mango##1
6. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Food     | papaya      | mango       | zucchini | blueberry     |

