.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, rock, electronic, ambient
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
3. the fan of rock is between the entrepreneur and the fan of classical##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Music-Genre   | ambient          | rock | classical         | electronic  |

 